warmups — vendored codeviz assets and attribution
=================================================

These files are vendored (copied) from codeviz
(https://github.com/manzoid/codeviz) so warmups can run the Python live tracer
in the browser via Pyodide and render traces offline. They are imported at build
time via Vite `?raw` imports. Do not edit them here; update codeviz and re-copy.

Files
-----
  pg_logger.py         Online Python Tutor (OPT) Python tracer
  pg_encoder.py        OPT heap/value encoder
  viewer_template.html codeviz's self-contained offline trace renderer

