codeviz renderer
----------------
  viewer_template.html

codeviz's own work, MIT-licensed. It is a self-contained offline page (inline
CSS + JS, no network). The trace JSON is injected by string replacement of the
`__TRACE_JSON__` and `__TITLE__` markers.
